OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FThe Queen and Princess of Wales have
OL,8,Fhailed Arthur Fery's Wimbledon victory
OL,9,Fa "fantastic achievement", as the
OL,10,FBritish wildcard for reaching the semi-
OL,11,Ffinals of the competition.
OL,13,FThe 23-year-old, who grew up only 10
OL,14,Fminutes from the All England Club,
OL,15,Fwhich is patroned by Katherine, beat
OL,16,FItalian ninth seed Flavio Cobolli on
OL,17,FCentre Court on Wednesday afternoon to
OL,18,Fmake it through to the semi-finals.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@YO]
