OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FCamilla, who made a surprise visit to
OL,8,FWimbledon, was seen supporting Fery
OL,9,Ffrom the royal box, wearing a
OL,10,Fturquoise chiffon dress by designer
OL,11,FAnna Valentine.
OL,13,FFollowing his emphatic win, Camilla
OL,14,Fjoined the rest of the crowd to give
OL,15,FFery a standing ovation, smiling as
OL,16,Fshe clapped along.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
