OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FAsked how he would be preparing for
OL,8,FFriday's semi-final, he said: "I don't
OL,9,Fknow as I've never been in this
OL,10,Fposition before.
OL,12,F"I'm just going to keep going, I've
OL,13,Fbeen doing a great for the last 10
OL,14,Fdays I'm just going to keep going and
OL,15,Fsee where that takes me."
OL,17,FFery dropped to the floor after his
OL,18,Fwinning ace, before walking up to the
OL,19,Fnet and shaking hands with his
OL,20,Fopponent.
OL,26,@pD@_OUtD@AOUwD@YO]
