OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FThe crowd erupted into loud cheers
OL,8,Fwith many onlookers standing to
OL,9,Fapplaud the player.
OL,11,FHis parents appeared emotional as they
OL,12,Fwatched alongside US actress Elle
OL,13,FFanning, and adventurer Bear Grylls,
OL,14,Famong others.
OL,16,FBettina and Clive Sanford, from north
OL,17,FLondon, watched the match on Centre
OL,18,FCourt after getting ballot tickets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
