OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FMrs Sanford said it has been a
OL,8,F"fantastic day" and praised Fery's
OL,9,F"calm" demeanour.
OL,11,FHer husband said the match was
OL,12,F"amazing", adding: "He just played
OL,13,Fwith confidence the whole time."
OL,15,FLiz Hardisty, from West Sussex, was
OL,16,Fsitting on Henman Hill when Fery made
OL,17,Fhis winning shot.
OL,19,FReacting to his victory, she said: "It
OL,20,Fwas really exciting and I'm glad I
OL,21,Fcame...
