OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,F"It was worth coming just to see him,
OL,8,Fsuch an underdog, a wild card to get
OL,9,Fto the semi-final ` it's virtually
OL,10,Funheard of."
OL,12,FThe Princess of Wales congratulated
OL,13,FFery on his win and wished him luck
OL,14,Ffor the semi-final.
