OL,3,CQueen and Princess of Wales hail
OL,4,CArthur Fery as he reaches Wimbledon
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FShe wrote on X: "A memorable day at
OL,8,FWimbledon. Congratulations to Arthur
OL,9,FFery on becoming the first British
OL,10,Fwildcard to reach the Gentlemen's
OL,11,FSingles semi-finals in the Open Era, a
OL,12,Ffantastic achievement that has
OL,13,Finspired so many. Wishing you the very
OL,14,Fbest for the next round."
OL,16,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer posted
OL,17,Fon X: "What a moment for Arthur Fery.
OL,18,FFrom wild card to Wimbledon semi-
OL,19,Ffinalist, a brilliant performance on
OL,20,Fthe biggest stage. Best of luck in
OL,21,Fyour next match!"
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@YO]yD@GOU}D@QO]
